spec_data.Name: python2-requests-file
spec_data.Description:
Requests-File is a transport adapter for use with the Requests Python
library to allow local file system access via file:// URLs.

This is the Python 2 version of the requests_file module
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Sat 29 Jul 2017 03:32:45 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Transport adapter for using file:// URLs with python-requests
